title: 10-manbun no 1
attributes: Rank: 81159th, it has 232 monthly / 15K total views.
summary: 1/100 000 – A story about a destiny between the lines of cruelty and joy 2nd year high school student Rino Sakuragi has been in love with Ren Kiritani, a member of her friends-circle since junior high. Rino, who cannot love either her character nor body, is incredibly shy towards the popular Kiritani. “Being friends suits me just fine. After all, I don’t want to be hated once he gets to know the real me…” Even though she’s resigned herself to that, she cannot help but stay in love with Kiritani as he keeps on dropping suggestive lines like “Cute.” or “What do you think about me?”… “I want the person I love to really get to know the real me. But because it’s the person I love, I need more courage!!” 1/100 000 – A story about a destiny between the lines of cruelty and joy by the master of pure love romance Kaho Miyasaka.
